       PROCESS NOMONOPRC.
       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. GEMCBLPGM.
      *======================================================================
      * Program: GEMCBLPGM (COBOL Version)
      * Description: SQLCBLLE wrapper for GEMINI_QUERY using SQL to read
      *              the data area for the API key.
      *
      * Compilation:
      *   CRTSQLCBLI OBJ(YOURLIB/GEMCBLPGM) 
      *              SRCSTMF('/path/to/GEMCBLPGM.sqlcblle')
      *              COMMIT(*NONE) OBJTYPE(*PGM) CVTCCSID(*JOB)
      *======================================================================
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       SOURCE-COMPUTER. IBM-I.
       OBJECT-COMPUTER. IBM-I.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA END-EXEC.

       01  WS-SQL-VARS.
           05  H-MODEL         PIC X(100).
           05  H-KEY           PIC X(100).
           05  H-CONTENT       PIC X(5000).
           05  H-RESULT        PIC X(32000).

       01  WS-VARIABLES.
           05  WS-DTAARA-NAME  PIC X(10) VALUE "GEMINIKEY".
           05  WS-IDX          PIC S9(4) COMP.

       LINKAGE SECTION.
       01  P-MODEL             PIC X(100).
       01  P-CONTENT           PIC X(5000).
       01  P-RESULT            PIC X(5000).

       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING P-MODEL P-CONTENT P-RESULT.
       MAIN-LOGIC.
      * Initialize result
           MOVE SPACES TO P-RESULT.

      * Override with parameters if provided
           IF P-MODEL = SPACES
               MOVE "gemini-2.5-flash" TO H-MODEL
           ELSE
               MOVE P-MODEL TO H-MODEL
           END-IF.

           IF P-CONTENT = SPACES
               MOVE "What is IBM i?" TO P-CONTENT
           ELSE
      * Sanitize command-line garbage by replacing control chars with spaces
               PERFORM VARYING WS-IDX FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL WS-IDX > 5000
                   IF P-CONTENT(WS-IDX:1) < SPACE
                       MOVE SPACE TO P-CONTENT(WS-IDX:1)
                   END-IF
               END-PERFORM
           END-IF.
           
      * Build JSON content
           MOVE SPACES TO H-CONTENT
           STRING '{"contents":[{"parts":[{"text":"' DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  FUNCTION TRIM(P-CONTENT) DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  '"}]}]}' DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  INTO H-CONTENT
           END-STRING.

      * Read API key from Data Area using SQL
           MOVE SPACES TO H-KEY.
           EXEC SQL
               SELECT TRIM(DATA_AREA_VALUE)
               INTO :H-KEY
               FROM TABLE(QSYS2.DATA_AREA_INFO(DATA_AREA_NAME
                => :WS-DTAARA-NAME))
           END-EXEC.

           IF SQLCODE NOT = 0 OR H-KEY = SPACES
              DISPLAY "Error: API key not found in data area GEMINIKEY"
              GOBACK
           END-IF.

      * Call the GEMINI_QUERY function
           DISPLAY "--- DEBUG INFO ---"
           DISPLAY "MODEL:   " H-MODEL(1:50)
           DISPLAY "CONTENT1:" H-CONTENT(1:100)
           DISPLAY "CONTENT2:" H-CONTENT(101:100)
           DISPLAY "CONTENT3:" H-CONTENT(201:100)
           DISPLAY "------------------"
           MOVE SPACES TO H-RESULT.
           EXEC SQL
               SELECT CAST(GEMINI_QUERY(
                   TRIM(:H-MODEL),
                   TRIM(:H-KEY),
                   TRIM(:H-CONTENT)
               ) AS VARCHAR(32000))
               INTO :H-RESULT
               FROM SYSIBM.SYSDUMMY1
           END-EXEC.

           IF SQLCODE = 0
              DISPLAY "Success"
              MOVE H-RESULT(1:5000) TO P-RESULT
           ELSE
              DISPLAY "Error calling GEMINI_QUERY. SQLSTATE: " SQLSTATE
              MOVE "ERROR" TO P-RESULT
           END-IF.

           GOBACK.
